<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Virtual Lost and Found</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Body and General Layout */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f4f7fb; /* Light greyish background */
        }

        /* Left Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            width: 350px; /* Increased width */
            background-color: #2C3E50; /* Deep Blue color */
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 100%;
            box-shadow: 2px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 25px;
            z-index: 100;
            overflow-y: auto; /* Ensures sidebar content is scrollable */
        }

        .sidebar h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .sidebar p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        /* Action Boxes */
        .action-box {
            background-color: #34495E; /* Darker Blue for action box */
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            min-height: 250px; /* Increased height */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px; /* Added gap between buttons */
        }

        .sidebar a, .sidebar button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #ECF0F1; /* Light background for buttons */
            color: #2C3E50; /* Deep Blue Text */
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover, .sidebar button:hover {
            background-color: #BDC3C7;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Content Area */
        .content {
            margin-left: 370px; /* Space for sidebar */
            padding: 30px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        /* Information Section */
        .info-section {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .info-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .info-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .info-section li {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #2C3E50;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                position: relative;
                padding-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .content {
                margin-left: 0;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .sidebar button, .sidebar a {
                width: auto;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Left Sidebar -->
    <div class="sidebar">
        <h1>Virtual Lost and Found</h1>
        <p>Welcome, <%= username %></p>

        <% if (success) { %>
            <div style="color: green; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <%= success %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <!-- Action Section -->
        <div class="action-box">
            <form action="/report-lost" method="GET">
                <button type="submit">Report a Lost Item</button>
            </form>
            <form action="/search-lost" method="GET">
                <button type="submit">Search for Lost Items</button>
            </form>
            <a href="/my-lost-items">View My Reported Items</a>
            <form action="/logout" method="POST">
                <button type="submit">Logout</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Content Area -->
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Safety & Responsibilities</h2>
        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>How to Use the Virtual Lost and Found</h3>
            <p>This platform helps you report lost items, search for lost items, and view your reported items. Please keep the following tips in mind:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Be Honest:</strong> Provide accurate information about lost or found items to help others.</li>
                <li><strong>Be Safe:</strong> Meet in public places if exchanging items, for your own safety.</li>
                <li><strong>Be Responsible:</strong> Take care of items you find and ensure they are returned to the rightful owner.</li>
                <li><strong>Follow the Law:</strong> Always comply with local laws when reporting or retrieving lost items.</li>
                <li><strong>Report Immediately:</strong> If you find an item, report it as soon as possible to help others track it down.</li>
                <li><strong>Stay Vigilant:</strong> Report any suspicious activities to the authorities to keep the community safe.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>More Information</h3>
            <p>If you're looking for lost items, you can easily browse through the reported items or search by categories. Here are some additional tips:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Categories:</strong> Lost items are categorized for easier searching, such as electronics, clothing, and documents.</li>
                <li><strong>Photos:</strong> Upload clear pictures of the lost or found item for better identification.</li>
                <li><strong>Notify the Owner:</strong> If you find an item, try to notify the owner immediately to ensure a smooth return.</li>
                <li><strong>Timely Updates:</strong> Keep the platform updated with the latest information on any item you find or lose.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h3>Lost Item Reporting</h3>
            <p>When reporting a lost item, make sure to provide as many details as possible, such as the itemâ€™s condition, location, and time of loss. The more information you provide, the easier it is for others to help you.</p>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Virtual Lost and Found | All Rights Reserved</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
